      "message": "this is a fairly typical pattern:\n* https://godoc.org/cloud.google.com/go/spanner#NewClient and https://godoc.org/cloud.google.com/go/spanner#ReadOnlyTransaction.Query\n* https://godoc.org/cloud.google.com/go/bigquery#NewClient and https://godoc.org/cloud.google.com/go/bigquery#Query.Read\n\nso I think this change should be reverted",
