      "side": 1,
      "message": "it is used only in TestServer. Would be much simpler to write\n\n  addr, cleanup :\u003d installTestListener(srv)\n  So(srv.Start(), ShouldBeNil)\n  defer cleanup()\n\nin L104. Then all sub-conveys would already have a started server\n\nand stepping back, same with installtestListener really",
      "range": {
